text: There is no value shift happening from big tech (Apple, Google, MSFT, Amazon) to these decentralized companies. Someday if crypto, NFT, blockchain, metaverse etc becomes a technology from where stable and value based returns can be made, these big tech companies will absolutely crush everyone to become market leaders in them. So the safe bet is not to invest in volatile things like crypto, nfts etc. Just stay invested in Google, MSFT, Amazon, Apple, Meta etc. In the dotcom era, there was a value shift which happened because internet has probably been the biggest value add in human lives in the last 500 or so years (in addition to critical vaccines and antibiotics), so any company which had a huge vision based on internet(like Amazon, Facebook) or companies who were smart enough to see that change (MSFT, Apple), made a lot of money by building and using internet. There wont be any value shift which will happen from these companies unless there is a massive advancement in AI which these companies fail to see or monetize on (which is highly unlikely), as they are also the market leaders in AI.
